#: weblate/trans/models/announcement.py:171
msgid "Message"
msgstr "Teachtaireacht"

#: weblate/accounts/forms.py:661
msgid ""
"Please contact us in English. Otherwise, we might not process your request."
msgstr ""
"Déan teagmháil linn i mBéarla le do thoil. Seachas sin, seans nach "
"ndéanfaimid d'iarratas a phróiseáil."

#: weblate/accounts/forms.py:686 weblate/accounts/templatetags/authnames.py:34
