msgstr ""
"Scriosfar gach aip fíordheimhnithe a cumraíodh roimhe seo nuair a fhíorófar "
"an aip nua."

#: weblate/accounts/forms.py:1218
msgid ""
"Other two-factor methods (such as WebAuthn and security keys) won't be "
