#: weblate/templates/trans/merge_instructions.html:8
msgid ""
"The exported Weblate repository can be shallow by default, so this workflow "
"works best from an up-to-date upstream checkout. Cloning from the exported "
"Weblate repository or using an outdated upstream checkout can fail even when "
"Weblate and upstream are in sync. See the FAQ below for details."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leis an stórlann Weblate onnmhairithe a bheith éadomhain de réir "
"réamhshocraithe, mar sin oibríonn an sreabhadh oibre seo is fearr ó "
"sheiceáil amach suas an tsrutha atá cothrom le dáta. Is féidir le clónáil ón "
"stórlann Weblate onnmhairithe nó úsáid a bhaint as seiceáil amach suas an "
"tsrutha atá as dáta teip fiú nuair a bhíonn Weblate agus an t-uas an tsrutha "
"sioncrónaithe. Féach ar na Ceisteanna Coitianta thíos le haghaidh sonraí."

#: weblate/templates/trans/merge_instructions.html:12
msgid ""
"Open an existing checkout of the upstream repository or perform a fresh one."
msgstr ""
"Oscail seiceáil amach reatha den stór in aghaidh an tsrutha nó déan ceann úr."

